Q1) Manage Identity Providers

Configure OAuth to use HTPasswd as Identity Provider

Secret name: ex280-secure

IDP name: ex280-idp-secure

Create user bob with password indionce

Create user qwerty with password catalog

Create user john with password john123

Create user armstrong with password natasha123

Create user natasha with password arthstrong

Create user harry with password harry123

Create user susan with password susuan123

Q2) Manage Cluster Project and Permissions

Create projects: apollo, test, demo

bob user: cluster-admin rights

john user: can create projects

qwerty user: can create projects

natasha: can view only apollo and test

armstrong: admin of apollo

kubeadmin: should not exist (delete kubeadmin)

Q3) Managing Groups

Create groups: site-users, guest-users

Add qwerty user to guest-users

Add harry and susan users to site-users

Give edit permission to site-users on test project

Give view permission to guest-users on demo project

