Q10) Create Secure Route in quart project

App hello already running (http)

Route name: htquart

Must serve HTTPS using a self-signed certificate
openssl req -x509 -nodes -days 365 -newkey rsa:2048 -keyout tls.key -out tls.crt
Certificate subject:

/C=US/ST=North Carolina/L=Raleigh/O=RedHat/CN=quart.apps.ocp4.example.com


Secure URL:

https://quart.apps.domain3.example.com


Application must produce output

