Q20) Create NetworkPolicy to connect two pods

One pod in database namespace

One pod in checker namespace

Pod in checker must access database pod

NetworkPolicy name: mysql-db-conn

Use namespace label: team=devsecops

Use pod label: deployment=web-mysq

Port: 3306/tcp

Verify using checker pod logs

Q21) Create a Liveness Probe in project tuesday

Port: 8443

Initial delay: 3 seconds

Timeout: 10 seconds

Must survive 3 crashes (failureThreshold=3)

